About Us

Welcome to Corrado's Cucina, a new Italian restaurant & pizzeria conveniently located at the intersection of Arthur Kill Rd and Richmond Ave. in the Great Kills area of Staten Island. As a family-owned and operated establishment, we take pride in offering a dining experience that captures the essence of home-cooked meals and cherished family gatherings. From mouthwatering Neapolitan-style pizzas with perfectly crispy crusts to savory pasta dishes that melt in your mouth, our menu features items that cater to the young and old alike.

Private Events

CELEBRATE YOUR NEXT EVENT WITH US!

Our private event space at Corrado’s Cucina is the ideal space for mid-size parties, perfect for occasions such as birthdays, baby showers, bridal showers, and office gatherings. Equipped with an 85” screen and an advanced audiovisual system, it’s the perfect canvas for your party needs, whether you’re sharing photo slideshows, personal videos, or hosting business presentations. It’s also an ideal spot for watching sports events with friends and family, making it a multifunctional space for all your celebration needs.

Our Menu

At Corrado’s Cucina, we believe that the best meals are the ones shared with family and friends. Our menu features a delectable selection of classic Italian dishes. From the perfectly baked Neapolitan pizza, to indulgent pasta creations, we have something to satisfy everyone at the table. 

Menu

Step into our vibrant bar, adorned with high-top tables and large-screen TVs, creating the perfect setting for sports enthusiasts and social gatherings. We offer a well-curated selection of cocktails, wines and beer to satisfy your every craving. Whether you’re seeking a place to unwind, celebrate, or catch the game, we welcome you to join us to create memories at Corrado’s Cucina. 

Our Bar

Indulge in the true essence of Neapolitan-style pizza at Corrado's Cucina, available in both personal and full sizes. Our pizza menu offers a delightful array of red and white options, each crafted with the freshest ingredients and a commitment to authenticity. From traditional classics to innovative creations, we have something for every pizza lover.
